Invocation Name: breakfast idea generator
des: Have you ever felt like there are just too many options for breakfast. Well now there is a solution. Use the Breakfast Idea Generator to have the Amazon Alexa solve all of your problems. Each day, the Breakfast Idea Generator gives you new ideas for what to eat for breakfast.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
